Now if the 2000-hp monk kills FOUR bats in a row...well he'll have longer to regen up, but then he will have gotten more xp before he had to rest.  I can't see how more hps are less efficient for soloing. <p><a href="http://www.deadlyvirtues.com/" target="_blank">
