<br>
Remember, it works ALL the time, not just during fights.<br>
<br>
Average spider in velks takes 1500hps to kill. Fungi = 6 extra mobs per hour, or ~33% increase in exp.<br>
<br>
Hps = safety, and difficulty of mob<br>
but<br>
Regen = kill rate.<br>
<br>
<br>
All else being equal, a monk with 2.5k hps and fungi will exp much faster than a monk with 4.5k hps and no fungi.<br>
<br>
